<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{% block title %}{% endblock %}</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="{{ asset('images/icon.svg') }}">

    <!-- Raleway font from Google Fonts -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Raleway:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    {% block stylesheets %}
        {{ encore_entry_link_tags('app') }}
    {% endblock %}

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f9f5fb;
            color: #25282b;
        }

        .content {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 8px auto 0;
            padding: 16px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 4px;
            box-shadow: 2px 2px 8px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .content h1 {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #25282b;
        }
        .content p {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 200;
            color: #25282b;
        }
        .banner {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 8px auto 0;

            text-align: center;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: start;
        }
        .banner img {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-right: 8px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            box-shadow: 2px 2px 8px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .banner p {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0;
            color: #9900fe;
        }

        .footer {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 16px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            /*border-radius: 4px;
            box-shadow: 2px 2px 8px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);*/
            word-break: break-all;
        }
        .footer p{
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #5f6368;
        }
        .footer a{
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #d19cff;
        }
        .footer a:hover{
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #bb64ff;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Banner -->
    <div class="banner">
        <a href="https://www.klugesmanagement.at/">
            <img src="../../images/banner/banner1.jpg" alt="Kluges Management Banner">
        </a>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="content">
        <h1>Hallo {{ username }}</h1>
        {% block main_content %}{% endblock %}
    </div>

    <!-- Banner -->
    <div class="banner">
        <a href="https://www.klugesmanagement.at/">
            <img src="../../images/banner/banner2.jpg" alt="Kluges Management Banner">
        </a>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>Dies ist ein automatisch generiertes E-Mail des Nachhilfeinstituts [...] . Bitte antworten Sie nicht auf diese Nachricht und wenden Sie sich bei Fragen zum Inhalt direkt an den Versender.</p>
        <br>
        <p>
            <a href="https://www.klugesmanagement.at/">Kluges Management</a>, Max Mustermann Stra√üe, 1030 Wien,
            <a href="tel:067763792074">0666 123456 789</a>,
            <a href="mailto:office@klugesmanagement.at">office@klugesmanagement.at</a>
        </p>
        <p>Keine E-Mails mehr erhalten: <a href="#">Abmelden</a></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
